Retrobattle README
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a very brief readme, but it will hopefully help you somewhat.


Compiling
---------

1. Get remar2d and retro
   $ git clone git://github.com/remar/remar2d.git
   $ git clone git://github.com/remar/retro.git

2. Make remar2d
   $ cd remar2d/src
   $ make

3. Make retro
   $ cd ../../retro/src
   $ make


Compiling without SDL_Mixer
---------------------------

If you don't have SDL_Mixer you can compile without sound by doing two
simple things:

1. Edit the makefile in retro (retro/src/Makefile), uncomment the
   first LIBS line and comment the second LIBS line
2. Edit SoundManager.h (retro/src/SoundManager.h) and uncomment
   #define NO_SDL_MIXER


Run
---

1. To run, simply run the executable in retro/src
   $ cd retro/src
   $ ./retro


Contacting
